<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>DomaHub - Domain Name Rentals</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/min/main_index.min.css" />
  <meta name="description" content="DomaHub provides domain name rentals at low, affordable prices and flexible time slots. Rent one today!" />
  <%- include("../templates/head_links"); %>
</head>

<body>

  <%- include("../templates/navbar", {user: user}); %>
<!-- Background image source - https://unsplash.com/@avirichards -->
  <section id="index-img" class="section is-index-img">
    <div>

    </div>
    <div class="container flex-column-center">
      <div class="content has-text-centered">
        <h1 class="title is-1 is-white">
          Rent domain names.
        </h1>
        <h2 class="subtitle is-4 is-white">
          DomaHub is the marketplace for domain rentals offering
          quality domain names at flexible time slots.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="content has-text-centered">
        <a tabindex="1" href="#have_domains_section" id="have_domains_button" class="beta-submit button is-primary is-large margin-10" title="Sign Up">I have domains</a>
        <a tabindex="1" href="#want_domains_section" id="want_domains_button" class="beta-submit button is-primary is-inverted is-large margin-10" title="Sign Up">I want domains</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="has-text-centered">
      <p id="learn_more_text" style="opacity:0;" class="is-white">
          Learn more...
      </p>
      <span class="icon is-medium is-white margin-bottom-10">
          <i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i>
      </span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="have_domains_section" class="section is-medium">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column margin-bottom-25">
          <div class="content">
            <p class="is-blacklight is-bold heading">
              DOMAIN OWNERS
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="content">
            <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered">Don't let your domains rot away.</h1>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-5">
          <div class="content">
            <h2>Create a new revenue stream.</h2>
            <p>
              Why let your domains sit unused while you're looking for buyers?
              List them with us and you'll simply make money every time
              someone rents your domains.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="content">
            <h2>Generate meaningful traffic.</h2>
            <p>
              You don't have to park ads or break your back trying to generate
              traffic. Let someone else utilize your domain name and reach greater,
              larger audiences than ever before.
            </p>
            <a tabindex="1" href="/sellers" class="is-accent" title="Selling on DomaHub">
              <span>Learn more about selling on DomaHub</span>
              <span class="icon is-small v-align-bottom">
                <i class="fa fa-caret-right"></i>
              </span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-6 is-offset-1">
          <div class="content">
            <h2>A commission system that rewards you.</h2>
            <p>
              We offer a commission system with three tiers applied on a
              listing-to-listing basis. Every listing starts off with 18% commission
              which decreases with each successive level. The more popular your
              domain is, the lower its commission!
            </p>
            <table class="table has-shadow">
              <thead>
                <th>Level</th>
                <th>Rental Rate</th>
                <th>Commission</th>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td>1</td>
                  <td>0 - 25%</td>
                  <td>18%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>2</td>
                  <td>25 - 50%</td>
                  <td>16.5%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>3</td>
                  <td>50%+</td>
                  <td>15%</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
            <a tabindex="1" href="/faq#selling" class="is-accent" title="Go to FAQ">
              <span>Have questions? Consult our FAQ!</span>
              <span class="icon is-small v-align-bottom">
                <i class="fa fa-caret-right"></i>
              </span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section is-medium is-primary">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content margin-bottom-25">
        <h1 class="title is-2 is-white has-text-centered">Why list with DomaHub?</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content has-text-centered">
        <h3 class="is-white">
          Here are some of DomaHub's best features and benefits.
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-6">
          <div class="slider-box">
            <div class="slider-item">
              <div class="slider-content">
                <span class="slider-icon icon is-primary is-medium">
                  <i class="fa fa-id-card-o"></i>
                </span>
                <div class="content slider-text">
                  <h3>Always maintain ownership</h3>
                  <p>
                    Don't worry about transferring ownership.
                  </p>
                  <a class="slider-learn is-accent">Click to learn more.</a>
                </div>
                <div class="slider-hidden-content margin-right-25 slider-text">
                  <p>
                    No more dealing with the hassle of transferring ownership to
                    renters! By redirecting the renter's web content to your domain,
                    there is no ownership transfer and the whole process
                    is quick and efficient.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="slider-icon">
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-angle-right"></i>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="slider-box">
            <div class="slider-item">
              <div class="slider-content">
                <span class="slider-icon icon is-primary is-medium">
                  <i class="fa fa-dollar"></i>
                </span>
                <div class="content slider-text">
                  <h3>Full control over pricing</h3>
                  <p>
                    Configure pricing for each rental listing.
                  </p>
                  <a class="slider-learn is-accent">Click to learn more.</a>
                </div>
                <div class="slider-hidden-content margin-right-25 slider-text">
                  <p>
                    You get to decide the pricing for all of your listings.
                    The minimum price for all time rates is one dollar.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="slider-icon">
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-angle-right"></i>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-6">
          <div class="slider-box">
            <div class="slider-item">
              <div class="slider-content">
                <span class="slider-icon icon is-primary is-medium">
                  <i class="fa fa-calendar-check-o"></i>
                </span>
                <div class="content slider-text">
                  <h3>Decide domain availability</h3>
                  <p>
                    Choose daily, weekly, or monthly rental times.
                  </p>
                  <a class="slider-learn is-accent">Click to learn more.</a>
                </div>
                <div class="slider-hidden-content margin-right-25 slider-text">
                  <p>
                      Listings can be rented out by the day, week, or month.
                      Find the best time rate for your listing and feel free to change
                      it whenever you want!
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="slider-icon">
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-angle-right"></i>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="slider-item-dropdown">
              <div class="content">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="slider-box">
            <div class="slider-item">
              <div class="slider-content">
                <span class="slider-icon icon is-primary is-medium">
                  <i class="fa fa-credit-card"></i>
                </span>
                <div class="content slider-text">
                  <h3>Quick and easy payments</h3>
                  <p>
                    Get paid immediately and securely.
                  </p>
                  <a class="slider-learn is-accent">Click to learn more.</a>
                </div>
                <div class="slider-hidden-content margin-right-25 slider-text">
                    <p>
                        We use a payments processor called Stripe.
                        Stripe allows you to get paid quickly and securely.
                        For more information on payments visit <a target="_blank" href="https://www.stripe.com" class="is-accent">Stripe's website</a>
                        or read our <a target="_blank" href="/faq#payments" class="is-accent">FAQ.</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="slider-icon">
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-angle-right"></i>
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="want_domains_section" class="section is-medium">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column margin-bottom-25">
          <div class="content">
            <p class="is-blacklight is-bold heading">
              DOMAIN RENTERS
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="content">
            <h1 class="title is-2 has-text-centered">Make domains useful again.</h1>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-5">
          <div class="content">
            <h2>Why rent a domain?</h2>
            <p>
              Domain rentals are flexible and adjust to your needs and schedule.
              You may only need to use a domain for a day, a week, or even a couple
              of months. We can help you rent a domain for as long - or as short -
              as you please!
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="content">
            <h2>Renting is easy.</h2>
            <p>
              Simply find the domain name you wish to rent, choose your
              desired time slot(s), and then provide a link to your content
              or website. Your domain rental will now redirect to the provided link!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="column is-5 is-offset-1">
          <div class="content">
            <h2>The advantages of renting.</h2>
            <ul class="margin-top-15">
              <li>
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <span>Gain access to domains that are already registered.</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <span>Rent for the exact times that you need.</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <span>Pay a fraction of the cost of buying.</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="icon is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-check"></i>
                </span>
                <span>Start displaying your content immediately.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section is-medium is-primary">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content margin-bottom-25">
        <h1 class="title is-2 is-white has-text-centered">How can I use domain rentals?</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content has-text-centered">
        <h3 class="is-white">
          Below are some examples of how you can utilize a domain rental.
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-12">
          <div class="card-flex-wrap">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-image has-border-bottom padding-20 has-text-centered">
                <span class="icon is-large is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-list-alt"></i>
                </span>
              </div>
              <div class="card-content">
                <div class="content has-text-centered">
                  <h3 class="is-bold">Advertising</h3>
                  <p>
                    High traffic domains are perfect places for advertisements.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-image has-border-bottom padding-20 has-text-centered">
                <span class="icon is-large is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-line-chart"></i>
                </span>
              </div>
              <div class="card-content">
                <div class="content has-text-centered">
                  <h3 class="is-bold">Marketing</h3>
                  <p>
                    Rent a relevant domain name for a short-term marketing campaign.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-image has-border-bottom padding-20 has-text-centered">
                <span class="icon is-large is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-picture-o"></i>
                </span>
              </div>
              <div class="card-content">
                <div class="content has-text-centered">
                  <h3 class="is-bold">Web Content</h3>
                  <p>
                    Redirect images, gifs, articles, blogs, and anything else on the internet.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-image has-border-bottom padding-20 has-text-centered">
                <span class="icon is-large is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-briefcase"></i>
                </span>
              </div>
              <div class="card-content">
                <div class="content has-text-centered">
                  <h3 class="is-bold">Professional</h3>
                  <p>
                    Host a resume, portfolio, or business presentation on a unique domain.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-image has-border-bottom padding-20 has-text-centered">
                <span class="icon is-large is-primary">
                  <i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>
                </span>
              </div>
              <div class="card-content">
                <div class="content has-text-centered">
                  <h3 class="is-bold">eCards</h3>
                  <p>
                    Domain rentals are the perfect way to send someone a meaningful message.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section is-medium is-lighter">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-6">
          <div class="content">
            <h1 class="title is-2">Have any questions?</h1>
            <h2 class="subtitle is-5">
              Feel free to send us a message or explore the FAQ!
            </h2>
            <a tabindex="1" class="button is-primary is-large margin-5">
              <span class="icon">
                <i class="fa fa-commenting"></i>
              </span>
              <span>Chat with Us!</span>
            </a>
            <a tabindex="1" class="button is-accent is-large margin-5" href="/faq" target="_blank">
              <span class="icon">
                <i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i>
              </span>
              <span>Check out FAQ</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

    <%- include("../templates/footer"); %>
    <%- include("../templates/js_scripts"); %>
    <script src="/js/routes/main/main_index_logic.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="/js/routes/main/beta_signup_logic.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  </body>
</html>
